	<a name="85086282">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<h3>Familiarization with Embanet</h3><b>An important difference</b>.&nbsp; The Explorer view and the Classic view are not interchangeable.&nbsp;  For one thing, a folder can have links or icons in the top part, and these don't show up when a folder is in the top of a split view.&nbsp; So the explorer view will not have what some tutorials refer to in their body text, when the text is in the bottom of a split directory or in the preview pane of the explorer itself.&nbsp; There may be settings to jiggle this together properly.&nbsp; I haven't found them yet.<br>
